      "body" : "You could also just get rid of MIN_BLOCK_TO_RESPECT_WITH_MAX_TX_CHECK. The theoretical maximum number of transactions in a block is 16665 anyway, so 100000 transactions effectively already requires 7 blocks anyway. If someone wants to set a lower number of transactions, so bit it.\r\n\r\nThat would simplify this PR, and have clearer semantics.",
